{"type": "article", "id": 2988, "title": "Jasper Morrison设计的 Ando 杯", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-22T07:51:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232904gYD29bJ8loah0dxS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tAndo’s Glass 来自于 Koichi Ando 对于制作简单玻璃器皿的追求，为了实现这一想法，这位日本 Ando 画廊的老板邀请来了以极简主义风格著称的英国设计师 Jasper Morrison。Morrison 设计了高、矮两种版本的杯子，它们的共同特点，就是杯侧由下往上呈现出微微倾斜的态势。两款杯子都是在一家位于东京旧城区的玻璃坊里，由技艺精湛的工匠师手工吹制而成。这款作品已入选“<a href=\"http://www.g-mark.org/?locale=en\" target=\"_blank\">2014日本优秀设计奖（2014 Japan Good Design Award）</a>” TOP100 榜单。定价 20 英镑，<a href=\"http://www.jaspermorrisonshop.com/products/ando-s-glasses\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232903za4LDCrOgEcvixSQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232903KpQR16I2CbOFTBxw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.784375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232903tmAxXgZduFMToGpb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}